description:
Nanami Yachiyo is a veteran Magical Girl in Kamihama City. She is a college student who`s not affiliated with a team, preferring to instead work alone. She is very territorial and is strict toward Magical Girls from other areas, especially when their skills don`t measure up. Yachiyo has been documenting all of Kamihama City`s "rumors."
Source: Official site
name: Nanami Yachiyo
